videos.headline: UConn opens the second quarter with back-to-back 3s
videos.description: Paige Bueckers and Morgan Cheli splash consecutive 3-pointers for the UConn Huskies vs. Holy Cross.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn opens the second quarter with back-to-back 3s) 2024/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarah Strong's 22 points lift UConn to 7-0 start
videos.description: UConn's Sarah Strong scores 22 points to pace the Huskies to an 88-52 victory over Holy Cross.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Sarah Strong's 22 points lift UConn to 7-0 start) 2024/12/04 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Sarah Strong's 12 points help UConn to halftime lead
videos.description: The Huskies enter halftime with a lead, thanks in large part to Sarah Strong's 12 first-half points.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sarah Strong's 12 points help UConn to halftime lead) 2024/12/04 ESHEET
